00:38:52,050 --> 00:38:52,740
Why don't we just

573
00:38:52,740 --> 00:38:53,900
go to the city hospital?

574
00:38:54,780 --> 00:38:56,940
I'm exhausted, that's all.

575
00:38:58,050 --> 00:38:59,860
I just need more sleep.

576
00:38:59,860 --> 00:39:00,900
Listen to me, then.

577
00:39:01,780 --> 00:39:02,650
Drink some soup,

578
00:39:03,000 --> 00:39:05,355
or else I'll have to carry you
to the city hospital.

579
00:39:29,260 --> 00:39:30,650
I don't want to drink.

580
00:39:32,090 --> 00:39:33,010
One more mouthful.

581
00:39:35,090 --> 00:39:35,930
No.

582
00:39:47,740 --> 00:39:48,690
Hello, Jun?

583
00:39:48,690 --> 00:39:49,340
Nan.

584
00:39:49,340 --> 00:39:51,130
There's a guy at the workshop

585
00:39:51,130 --> 00:39:52,420
who insists that you fix his car.

586
00:39:53,050 --> 00:39:53,890
Go.

587
00:39:54,810 --> 00:39:56,288
- Okay, got it.
- Great.

588
00:40:01,650 --> 00:40:02,650
I'm going, then.

589
00:40:03,380 --> 00:40:04,570
I'll leave the soup here.

590
00:40:05,650 --> 00:40:06,820
Remember to drink some.

591
00:40:24,260 --> 00:40:25,170
Sorry

592
00:40:25,170 --> 00:40:26,010
for the delay.

593
00:40:26,260 --> 00:40:27,340
You're Qin Nan?

594
00:40:29,044 --> 00:40:30,380
What's wrong with your car?

595
00:40:30,900 --> 00:40:31,860
It's...

596
00:40:31,860 --> 00:40:33,090
There's a smoky smell,

597
00:40:33,090 --> 00:40:34,780
and the warning lights are on,

598
00:40:34,780 --> 00:40:35,780
so please take a look.

599
00:41:18,940 --> 00:41:19,780
What are you doing?

600
00:41:19,940 --> 00:41:20,860
Who let you do that?

601
00:41:20,860 --> 00:41:22,050
Give it back! It's mine!

602
00:41:22,088 --> 00:41:23,888
- Who let you do that?
- Give my phone back!

603
00:41:25,380 --> 00:41:27,260
What are you up to?
I knew you were fishy.

604
00:41:27,400 --> 00:41:28,570
Who let you take these photos?

605
00:41:28,570 --> 00:41:29,570
I'm just recording my life.

606
00:41:29,570 --> 00:41:31,220
(Delete)
What do you mean by that?

607
00:41:31,688 --> 00:41:33,170
What kind of life are you recording?

608
00:41:33,170 --> 00:41:34,780
More like violating privacy, you know?

609
00:41:34,780 --> 00:41:35,650
No.

610
00:41:35,650 --> 00:41:36,380
Stop recording.

611
00:41:36,380 --> 00:41:37,220
Stop.

612
00:41:37,380 --> 00:41:38,420
I'll be honest.

613
00:41:38,955 --> 00:41:41,044
I have over 300,000 followers
on social media.

614
00:41:41,088 --> 00:41:43,622
I know he's in trouble,
so I'm helping him to clear his name.

615
00:41:43,820 --> 00:41:44,570
Do you think

616
00:41:44,570 --> 00:41:45,690
he needs your help?

617
00:41:45,690 --> 00:41:46,780
I have over 300,000 followers.

618
00:41:46,780 --> 00:41:48,260
I've got social influence.

619
00:41:48,260 --> 00:41:49,170
I can help him.

620
00:41:50,570 --> 00:41:51,410
Hello.

621
00:41:51,755 --> 00:41:53,355
Do you still need to fix your car?

622
00:41:55,130 --> 00:41:56,050
Go ahead.

623
00:41:56,266 --> 00:41:57,377
I'm already here, anyway.

624
00:41:57,688 --> 00:41:59,420
If you want to fix your car,
I can do it.

625
00:42:00,780 --> 00:42:01,780
But stop taking photos.

626
00:42:18,500 --> 00:42:19,340
Nan.

627
00:42:19,900 --> 00:42:20,820
What's your plan now?

628
00:42:22,060 --> 00:42:22,900
What do you mean?

629
00:42:24,940 --> 00:42:26,700
You were about to file
for divorce, right?

630
00:42:28,060 --> 00:42:29,740
Then, your wife got into trouble.

631
00:42:30,300 --> 00:42:31,540
As decent people,

632
00:42:31,577 --> 00:42:32,600
we're obligated to help

633
00:42:32,820 --> 00:42:34,860
if someone is in trouble.

634
00:42:35,820 --> 00:42:38,020
But it's already over, right?

635
00:42:38,020 --> 00:42:39,100
The court's verdict is out.

636
00:42:40,355 --> 00:42:42,300
The court's verdict
might not be the truth.

637
00:42:47,180 --> 00:42:48,220
Think again, will you?

638
00:42:49,780 --> 00:42:51,700
You haven't been married for long.

639
00:42:52,540 --> 00:42:54,140
Do you really know her that well?

640
00:42:57,820 --> 00:42:58,700
I know her.

641
00:43:00,100 --> 00:43:01,300
More than anyone else does.

642
00:43:02,820 --> 00:43:03,660
I trust her.

643
00:43:06,500 --> 00:43:08,380
Since you trust her, I believe in you.

644
00:43:08,380 --> 00:43:09,700
If anyone dares to say

645
00:43:09,700 --> 00:43:11,380
anything rotten about you,

646
00:43:11,380 --> 00:43:12,420
I'll chase them all away.

647
00:43:35,100 --> 00:43:35,820
Hey, Mom.

648
00:43:35,820 --> 00:43:36,540
Qin Nan.

649
00:43:36,540 --> 00:43:37,540
When are you free?

650
00:43:37,540 --> 00:43:39,020
Can you come over?

651
00:43:39,020 --> 00:43:39,540
Don't panic.

652
00:43:39,540 --> 00:43:40,488
Tell me what happened.

653
00:43:40,740 --> 00:43:42,140
I need to talk to you.

654
00:43:42,140 --> 00:43:43,540
Just come over.

655
00:43:43,540 --> 00:43:44,140
Okay, got it.

656
00:43:44,140 --> 00:43:44,980
I'll be right over.

657
00:43:46,340 --> 00:43:47,540
Jun, I need to go.

658
00:43:47,755 --> 00:43:48,933
Take care of the workshop.

659
00:44:06,941 --> 00:44:11,701
♪There's a gray cloud in your eyes♪

660
00:44:13,681 --> 00:44:19,271
♪But I see a long letter
through the clouds♪

661
00:44:20,351 --> 00:44:26,521
♪You hide your emotions, staying silent♪

662
00:44:26,971 --> 00:44:32,041
♪I wish I could accompany you
back to the clear sky♪

663
00:44:33,561 --> 00:44:38,671
♪If I could capture your shadow♪

664
00:44:40,291 --> 00:44:45,641
♪I wouldn't mind wandering again♪

665
00:44:46,901 --> 00:44:53,291
♪Moreover, my light is in your life♪

666
00:44:53,611 --> 00:44:59,051
♪So I must trust in myself♪

667
00:44:59,641 --> 00:45:03,951
♪Please let me become you♪

668
00:45:04,121 --> 00:45:07,581
♪The secret that you can tell♪

669
00:45:07,581 --> 00:45:13,141
♪Becoming the gentle fragrance
that heals your past♪

670
00:45:13,141 --> 00:45:17,141
♪If fate insists on drenching you♪

671
00:45:17,431 --> 00:45:20,181
♪With a torrential downpour♪

672
00:45:20,581 --> 00:45:26,001
♪Don't be afraid, I am your soul's coat♪

673
00:45:26,301 --> 00:45:30,371
♪Please let me become you♪

674
00:45:30,841 --> 00:45:34,151
♪Believing in the proof of love♪

675
00:45:34,151 --> 00:45:39,781
♪Becoming the island
where every dream of yours rests♪

676
00:45:39,781 --> 00:45:43,941
♪Don't lament the lost scenery♪

677
00:45:44,231 --> 00:45:46,881
♪As time passes♪

678
00:45:47,531 --> 00:45:52,801
♪I will still be here♪

679
00:45:53,401 --> 00:46:00,351
♪Not forgetting to accompany you
to the edges of the rest of life♪
